---
import SectionSubtitle from "../ui/SectionSubtitle.astro";
---

<section
  id="fuer-wen-ich-arbeite"
  class="relative bg-white px-4 py-16 dark:bg-brand-dark sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute top-1/2 left-0 -translate-y-1/2 w-[40vw] h-[40vw] bg-brand-blue/5 blur-[140px] rounded-full"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <SectionSubtitle>Zielgruppe</SectionSubtitle>
        <h2
          class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
        >
          Passt das für uns?
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div
          class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-white/5 dark:ring-white/10"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-red-400"></div>

          <h3
            class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
          >
            <span
              class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 dark:bg-red-900/30 dark:text-red-400"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                class="w-5 h-5"
              >
                <path
                  d="M6.28 5.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l3.72 3.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l3.72-3.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 6.28 5.22z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Nicht das Richtige für Sie, wenn…
          </h3>

          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-400 shrink-0"
              ></span>
              <span class="text-base leading-relaxed"
                >Sie wollen mal schnell irgendwas mit KI, weil alle das machen</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-400 shrink-0"
              ></span>
              <span class="text-base leading-relaxed"
                >Reine Showcase-Projekte ohne echten Prozess- oder
                Ergebnis-Impact</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-400 shrink-0"
              ></span>
              <span class="text-base leading-relaxed"
                >Projekte ohne Entscheidungsfähigkeit, bei denen grundlegende
                Strukturfragen nicht angegangen werden sollen</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div
          class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-brand-blue/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-brand-blue/20 dark:bg-brand-blue/10 dark:ring-brand-blue/30"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-brand-blue"></div>

          <h3
            class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue dark:text-brand-blue-light mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
          >
            <span
              class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue dark:bg-brand-blue/20 dark:text-brand-blue-light"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
                class="w-5 h-5"
              >
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            Besonders passend, wenn…
          </h3>

          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"
              ></span>
              <span class="text-base leading-relaxed font-medium"
                >Sie haben klare Schmerzpunkte in wertschöpfenden Kernprozessen</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"
              ></span>
              <span class="text-base leading-relaxed font-medium"
                >Ihnen DSGVO, Sicherheit und Governance wichtig sind – Sie sind
                bereit, Verantwortung zu tragen</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"
              ></span>
              <span class="text-base leading-relaxed font-medium"
                >Sie sind bereit, interne Ressourcen für Change und Governance
                zu aktivieren</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-brand-blue hover:text-blue-500 dark:text-brand-gold dark:hover:text-brand-gold/80"
        >
          Mehr zu meiner Erfahrung <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
